view.name: Department Of Water And Power (DWP) - Performance Metrics
view.description: This dataset contains metrics that measure the operational performance of the Department of Water and Power. These metrics are used on a regular basis by the department and the Mayor to evaluate progress and inform decision making. Performance management forms the foundation of a data-driven culture of innovation and excellence in the City of Los Angeles.
